column6:
With the eyes of the Marvel Universe looking on...a baby is born! Its a rare occasion in the Marvel Universe, so be here for a genuine emotional event! And it doesn't end the way you might think. Jessica Jones and Luke Cage's life will never be the same again!!,2006,1
Guest-starring the New Avengers.
32 PGS./T+ SUGGESTED FOR TEENS AND UP...$2.99
